                        Stuart
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1948v08</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d17</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">17</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1948-02-11T07:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1948-02-11T07:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-02-11T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-02-11T07:00:00-05:00" n="17" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d17">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.20 Missions/2–1148: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-02-11T20:00:00+08:00">February 11, 1948—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 11—8:37 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>280. I understand that the United States has responsibilities other than those in
                    China and I shall be guided by your 212, February 9, <pb facs="0025" n="15" xml:id="pg_15"/> 8 p.m. In this connection, however, you may wish to see
                    latest plea from Wei for ammunition.…</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stuart</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
